        </item>
        <item>
            <title>纯电 Alfa Romeo Junior 香港试驾，集操控乐趣与舒适感于一身的小型 SUV</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/24/alfa-romeo-junior-hk-testdrive/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 04:44:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alfa Romeo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[junior]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[爱快罗密欧]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297848</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上个月在香港正式亮相的小型 SUV Alfa Romeo Junior 是该意大利汽车品牌推出的首款纯电动车，这款车最初命名为 &#8220;Milano&#8221;，但因意大利政府反对使用城市名称，最终更名为 &#8220;Junior&#8221;，借此向经典车型致敬。这款去年在欧洲开售，市场反应甚佳的紧凑型 SUV，香港将会是<span lang="ZH-TW">亚太地区首个推出</span><span lang="ZH-TW">的市场，而 </span>unwire.hk 刚刚亦安排了本地的 Alfa Romeo Junior 实车测试。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_1528180.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152928.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作为 Alfa Romeo 进军电动车市场的第一步，Junior 采用 Stellantis 集团的 e-CMP 平台，与 Jeep Avenger 和 Peugeot e-2008 等车型共享技术基础，并提供纯电 / 混能版本车型选择。外观设计上，车长仅 4,173mm 的 Junior 延续了 Alfa Romeo 的经典美学，前方鬼面罩保留标志性的 Scudetto 三角盾形设计，更加上品牌潦草字样更显独特。Junior 搭配 「3+3」 全 LED 矩阵头灯散发现代科技感。后门采用隐藏式后门把手，车尾「coda tronca」陡峭的线条十分令人熟悉，倒 U 型一体式尾灯与头灯设计相呼应，黑色饰条环绕尾灯的车尾则从 Giulia TZ 汲取灵感，具有更强的视觉层次。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299036 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170589.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299053 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170592.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Junior 拥有经特别设计的空气动力学车身及轻量化设计，全车仅重 1,545KG，为同级 SUV 车中最轻巧的车款，具备同级最佳的动态性能、操控性和灵活性。动力方面，Alfa Romeo Junior Launch 及 Sport Edition 均搭载 156 匹马力的马达，最大扭力 260Nm，0-100 km/h 加速约 9 秒。前轮驱动的 Junior 并搭载 54kWh 锂电池。Launch / Sport Edition 的 WLTP 续航里程可达 410 公里，在城市路况下更可达到 590 公里。充电方面，直流快充则支援最高 100kW 功率，从 20% 到 80% 充电约需 30 分钟。</p><figure id="attachment_1299071" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1299071" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170581.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1299071" class="wp-caption-text"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299040 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170622.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299046" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151937.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299048 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170606.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299041" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151052.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Junior 的行李厢容量达 400 公升，后座放平后可扩充至 1,265 公升，在同级车中颇具实用性。</p><p>内栊方面，Junior 驾驶舱充满品牌特色，配备双 10.25 吋萤幕：仪表显示器采用经典「望远镜」造型，中央触控萤幕角度略向驾驶倾斜，提升显觉效果及操作便利性。空调出风口灵感来自 Quadrifoglio 的四叶草标志，Sport Edition 更会提供镶空设计的 Sabelt 运动座椅，可选红黑皮革与麂皮材质，增添豪华氛围。Alfa D.N.A 驾驶模式（Dynamic、Natural、Advanced Efficiency），让驾驶者根据不同需要调整油门反应与转向手感，此外，它亦提供动能回收开关功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151842.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299042" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151607.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152252.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299038 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170615.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299037 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170599.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299049 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170651.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">中控下方的置物空间设有无线充电板及 2 个 USB 取电介面。</p><h2 data-start="0" data-end="25"><strong data-start="0" data-end="25">试驾体验：轻巧灵活，富操控乐趣而不失舒适感</strong></h2><p data-start="27" data-end="166">今次试驾嘅 Junior 是一款相当小巧的 SUV，车长约 4.1 米、车宽约 1.7 米、高度约 1.53 米，短小的车身非常适合市区行驶，亦可随意进出任何停车场。今次试驾路线包括港岛西区、南区浅水湾道同埋域多利道等弯多路窄嘅地方。Junior 车身动态相当灵活，軚盘的指向性亦非常准确，很适合应付这类双线双程、还可能要防备如巴士、旅游巴等大车偷位的路段。这款车虽然并非以性能作为卖点，但胜在操控方面非常出色，悬挂亦调校得宜，喺凹凸不平嘅路面上行驶，发挥很好的滤震，即使在应付中低速的连续弯位时，车身晃动亦没有很明显。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_152217.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299039 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p3170617.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166">动力方面，厂方公布 Junior 马力为 156 匹，试驾的时候它的电马达提供嘅即时动力和加速感轻松超越 3500cc 级别的汽油车，无论在置富上斜定系需要加速超车，车内载满乘客亦不会觉得动力不足。至于驾驶模式方面，呢部车有三个模式— Dynamic、Natural 和 Advanced Efficiency，在不同情况下可以切换使用。Dynamic 模式下，电门反应会更快，加速感较强，但唔会即刻变咗一架赛车，感觉上仍然很温和，唔会太过激烈。Advanced Efficiency 模式以节能为主会更加悭电，车辆会回收动能，减低能源消耗。整体来讲，这部车的电门反应唔会太过敏感，驾驶感觉偏柔，适合长时间驾驶，富有驾驶乐趣和舒适感并存。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151715.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_151728.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p data-start="27" data-end="166">外观方面，它的设计很有科技感，特别系个倒三角色鬼面罩和 LED 头灯，睇落唔单止时尚更有独特性，不容易同其他市面上嘅电动车撞样。美中不足的是此车后座较窄，后座中间设有马鞍位，如果成人坐喺后排中间，应该会觉得有啲辛苦，比较适合小朋友。总体来讲，呢部小型 SUV 适合小家庭日常代步的电动车，尤其喺市区驾驶时好灵活，操控轻松，外观时尚，很适合作为油转电的第一台电动车。</p><p data-start="27" data-end="166"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299051" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250317_154156.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>ALFA ROMEO JUNIOR </strong><strong>规格表</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>售价: $359,800( Launch Edition) / $429,800 (Sport Edition)</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1299031 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe-675x900.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/alfaromeojuniorhkspe-435x580.jpg 435w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
